{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NjYwNA_0008","text":"你 知否我的心 多想愛一生 從沒有想過別人","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["忠貞的愛","對愛情的堅守","失望"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["知否","心","愛一生","別人"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,9,5,3,3,3,9,4,3,3,0,2,5,9,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","zi1","fau2","ngo5","dik1","sam1","do1","soeng2","oi3","jat1","sang1","cung4","mut6","jau5","soeng2","gwo3","bit6","jan4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"知否","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"多想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"從","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"想過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"別人","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"反問伴侶是否知道自己的心意，強調自己對愛情的忠貞。"},"source":{"title":"變心","artists":["陳慧嫺"],"lyricists":["潘源良"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6604","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NjYwNA_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn5ai0_NjYwNA_0009","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
